    "title": "Speed Post India is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Speed Post India! We are hiring a Warehouse Manager for our Vadodara team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Speed Post India:\nSpeed Post India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Speed Post India!",
